result.name: annual-survey-of-newly-qualified-teachers
result.notes: Annual survey of newly qualified teachers' perceptions of the quality of their training and how well it prepared them for their first teaching post. Each new cohort of newly qualified teachers is surveyed six months after completion of their initial teacher training. Data are published at sector and provider level (where the number of returns exceeds eleven).

organization.name: national-college-for-teaching-and-leadership
organization.title: National College for Teaching and Leadership
organization.description: Created on 1 April 2013, when the "National College  for Leadership of Schools and Children's Services" merged with the "Teaching Agency" to become the "National College for Teaching and Leadership".
